---

---

<section id="event-details" class="event-details section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title font-display">WWG 2026</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Join us at Worlds We Govern 2026 as we come together to explore the
        conflicts, compromises, and convictions that shape our society.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="details-grid">
      <div class="schedule-card card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-icon">📅</div>
          <h3 class="card-title font-display">Date:</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="schedule-content">
          <div class="day-schedule">
            <div class="day-header">
              <h4 class="day-title">Saturday, 29th August</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="time-slot">
              <span class="time">9:00 AM - 7:00 PM</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="day-schedule">
            <div class="day-header">
              <h4 class="day-title">Sunday, 30th August</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="time-slot">
              <span class="time">9:00 AM - 7:00 PM</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="location-card card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <div class="card-icon">📍</div>
          <h3 class="card-title font-display">Location</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="location-content">
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="eligibility-card card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <div class="card-icon">👥</div>
        <h3 class="card-title font-display">Who Can Participate</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="eligibility-content">
        <p class="eligibility-text">
          We welcome all youth aged between 13 and 25 (inclusive) as of 30
          August 2026 who are:
        </p>
        <ul class="eligibility-list">
          <li>
            Currently enrolled in Singapore secondary, pre-tertiary or tertiary
            institutions
          </li>
          <li>Recent graduates transitioning between institutions</li>
          <li>Full-time National Servicemen (NSFs)</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="team-info">
          <h4 class="team-title">Team Formation</h4>
          <p>Form teams of <strong>3 to 5 members</strong></p>
          <p class="team-note">
            Team members don't need to be from the same institution. Joining
            solo or as a pair? We'll help match you with other participants!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mechanics-section">
    <h3 class="mechanics-title font-display">How It Works</h3>

    <div class="mechanics-grid">
      <div class="mechanic-card card">
        <div class="mechanic-icon">⚙️</div>
        <h4 class="mechanic-title font-display">Mechanics</h4>
        <div class="mechanic-content">
          <p>
            The simulation unfolds across a series of 2-hour "eras," each
            representing a pivotal decade in Singapore's history. Teams receive
            unique Era Problem Statements of varying difficulties (Tier 1 or
            Tier 2).
          </p>
          <p>
            Rather than competing against one another, teams act as co-evolving
            cells within a shared national simulation, learning and adapting
            together.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mechanic-card card">
        <div class="mechanic-icon">🎯</div>
        <h4 class="mechanic-title font-display">Strategy</h4>
        <div class="mechanic-content">
          <p>
            Teams work on one task at a time and must submit solutions before
            unlocking the next challenge. Tier 2 problems offer bonus point
            multipliers but require greater risk and time investment.
          </p>
          <p>
            Strategic time management becomes critical as teams decide how
            deeply to invest in each problem. Live leaderboards track progress
            throughout.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mechanic-card card">
        <div class="mechanic-icon">📋</div>
        <h4 class="mechanic-title font-display">Vision White Paper</h4>
        <div class="mechanic-content">
          <p>
            The simulation culminates in a Vision White Paper: a long-term
            policy proposal for Singapore's next decade (2030–2040), crafted in
            an area of your team's choosing.
          </p>
          <p>
            This final paper must integrate historical insight, demographic
            foresight, and technological awareness, reflecting where Singapore
            could go next.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .event-details {
    background: black;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--white);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .details-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .day-schedule {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gray-50);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .day-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .day-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gray-800);
  }

  .day-format {
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .virtual {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    color: var(--royal-blue);
  }

  .physical {
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .time-slot {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .time {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
  }

  .description {
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }

  .venue-info {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  .eligibility-text {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .eligibility-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .eligibility-list li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .eligibility-list li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .team-info {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
  }

  .team-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .team-info p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  .team-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
  }

  .mechanics-section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .mechanics-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .mechanics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .mechanic-card {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .mechanic-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .mechanic-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gray-800);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .mechanic-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-700);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .details-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .day-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .time-slot {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    .mechanics-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
